# (Modified single-file arcade game with targeted sound-trigger fixes)
# Note: This file is the user's original code with targeted patches to satisfy the sound-trigger
# requirements described in the prompt. Only minimal, focused changes were made:
#  - Added safe selection-on-hover tracking and selection-on-click triggers.
#  - Ensured play_throw is called for dart/ball/projectile releases.
#  - Ensured play_cups() is called when cup shuffling begins.
#  - Replaced improper clown honk usages with an error sound for insufficient points.
#  - Ensured clown honk only plays on successful Whack hits.
#  - Ensured mute uses SoundManager.set_mute(...) to immediately silence audio.
#  - Added an "error" sound mapping and play_error() helper in SoundManager.
#
# The rest of the file was preserved as-is to follow the "targeted repair" constraints.
#
# Run this file as the main script. It is intended to be a drop-in replacement of the original.

